{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775847426943,"sessionID":"ses_2873fd99bffeD3IZMIHmfvsaUp","part":{"id":"prt_d78c147f4001UKiywVB6zCvzU7","messageID":"msg_d78c12c17001JBR4q7SEYMXhbg","sessionID":"ses_2873fd99bffeD3IZMIHmfvsaUp","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-fa26c87efc98426b872e3d7d784ed098","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/deployment/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/deployment/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Delta Spec: AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime Type Definition\n2: \n3: **Module:** `pkg/apis`  \n4: **Language:** Go  \n5: **Size:** S\n6: \n7: ---\n8: \n9: ## GIVEN/WHEN/THEN Scenarios\n10: \n11: ### Requirement: Package structure and registration\n12: \n13: The system SHALL define the `AgentRuntime` and `AgentRuntimeList` types in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` with proper package structure, scheme registration, and CRD markers for controller-gen.\n14: \n15: #### Scenario: Package structure exists\n16: - **GIVEN** the repository root at `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube`\n17: - **WHEN** examining `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n18: - **THEN** the directory SHALL contain:\n19:   - `doc.go` with `+k8s:deepcopy-gen=package` marker\n20:   - `register.go` with `SchemeGroupVersion` set to `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`\n21:   - `agentruntime_types.go` with `AgentRuntime` and `AgentRuntimeList` types\n22:   - `codeinterpreter_types.go` with `CodeInterpreter` and `CodeInterpreterList` types\n23:   - `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` (generated)\n24: \n25: #### Scenario: Scheme group version is correct\n26: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go`\n27: - **WHEN** reading the file\n28: - **THEN** `SchemeGroupVersion` SHALL be `schema.GroupVersion{Group: \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", Version: \"v1alpha1\"}`\n29: \n30: #### Scenario: Group version kind registration\n31: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go`\n32: - **WHEN** the `addKnownTypes` function is invoked\n33: - **THEN** it SHALL register `AgentRuntime`, `AgentRuntimeList`, `CodeInterpreter`, and `CodeInterpreterList` with the scheme\n34: \n35: ---\n36: \n37: ### Requirement: AgentRuntime type definition\n38: \n39: The system SHALL define `AgentRuntime` as a Kubernetes-style typed object with `TypeMeta`, `ObjectMeta`, `Spec`, and `Status`.\n40: \n41: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime struct shape\n42: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go`\n43: - **WHEN** reading the `AgentRuntime` struct definition\n44: - **THEN** the struct SHALL embed `metav1.TypeMeta` and `metav1.ObjectMeta` and have `Spec AgentRuntimeSpec` and `Status AgentRuntimeStatus` fields with JSON tags `spec` and `status`\n45: \n46: #### Scenario: AgentRuntimeList struct shape\n47: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go`\n48: - **WHEN** reading the `AgentRuntimeList` struct definition\n49: - **THEN** the struct SHALL embed `metav1.TypeMeta`, have `metav1.ListMeta` with JSON tag `metadata`, and `Items []AgentRuntime` with JSON tag `items`\n50: \n51: #### Scenario: CRD markers on AgentRuntime\n52: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go`\n53: - **WHEN** examining type-level markers\n54: - **THEN** the `AgentRuntime` type SHALL have:\n55:   - `+genclient` marker\n56:   - `+k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object` marker\n57:   - `+kubebuilder:object:root=true` marker\n58:   - `+kubebuilder:subresource:status` marker\n59: \n60: ---\n61: \n62: ### Requirement: AgentRuntimeSpec definition\n63: \n64: The system SHALL define `AgentRuntimeSpec` with required fields for session management and pod templating.\n65: \n66: #### Scenario: AgentRuntimeSpec fields\n67: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go`\n68: - **WHEN** reading the `AgentRuntimeSpec` struct\n69: - **THEN** the struct SHALL contain fields:\n70:   - `MaxSessionDuration string` with JSON tag `maxSessionDuration`\n71:   - `SessionTimeout string` with JSON tag `sessionTimeout`\n72:   - `TargetPort []TargetPort` with JSON tag `targetPort`\n73:   - `PodTemplate PodTemplateSpec` with JSON tag `podTemplate`\n74: \n75: #### Scenario: AgentRuntimeSpec required fields\n76: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go`\n77: - **WHEN** examining the `AgentRuntimeSpec` struct markers\n78: - **THEN** the struct SHALL have `+kubebuilder:validation:Required` or equivalent kubebuilder markers for `maxSessionDuration`, `sessionTimeout`, `targetPort`, and `podTemplate` fields\n79: \n80: #### Scenario: MaxSessionDuration default\n81: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go`\n82: - **WHEN** examining the `MaxSessionDuration` field marker\n83: - **THEN** it SHALL have `+kubebuilder:default=\"8h\"` marker\n84: \n85: #### Scenario: SessionTimeout default\n86: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go`\n87: - **WHEN** examining the `SessionTimeout` field marker\n88: - **THEN** it SHALL have `+kubebuilder:default=\"15m\"` marker\n89: \n90: ---\n91: \n92: ### Requirement: TargetPort type definition\n93: \n94: The system SHALL define `TargetPort` to specify how traffic is routed to the agent runtime pod.\n95: \n96: #### Scenario: TargetPort struct fields\n97: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go`\n98: - **WHEN** reading the `TargetPort` struct\n99: - **THEN** the struct SHALL contain:\n100:   - `Port int32` with JSON tag `port` (required)\n101:   - `Protocol ProtocolType` with JSON tag `protocol` (enum: HTTP, HTTPS)\n102:   - `Name string` with JSON tag `name` (optional)\n103:   - `PathPrefix string` with JSON tag `pathPrefix` (optional)\n104: \n105: #### Scenario: ProtocolType enum definition\n106: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go`\n107: - **WHEN** reading the `ProtocolType` type definition\n108: - **THEN** it SHALL be a string type with `+kubebuilder:validation:Enum=HTTP;HTTPS` marker and constants `ProtocolHTTP` and `ProtocolHTTPS`\n109: \n110: ---\n111: \n112: ### Requirement: AgentRuntimeStatus definition\n113: \n114: The system SHALL define `AgentRuntimeStatus` with standard Kubernetes condition fields.\n115: \n116: #### Scenario: AgentRuntimeStatus fields\n117: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go`\n118: - **WHEN** reading the `AgentRuntimeStatus` struct\n119: - **THEN** the struct SHALL contain `Conditions []metav1.Condition` with JSON tag `conditions`\n120: \n121: #### Scenario: Conditions field markers\n122: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go`\n123: - **WHEN** examining the `Conditions` field\n124: - **THEN** it SHALL have:\n125:   - `+kubebuilder:validation:Optional` marker\n126:   - `+listType=map` marker\n127:   - `+listMapKey=type` marker\n128: \n129: ---\n130: \n131: ### Requirement: DeepCopy generation\n132: \n133: The system SHALL generate `DeepCopy` methods for all types using controller-gen.\n134: \n135: #### Scenario: DeepCopyInto for AgentRuntime\n136: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go` (after `make generate`)\n137: - **WHEN** examining generated code\n138: - **THEN** `func (in *AgentRuntime) DeepCopyInto(out *AgentRuntime)` SHALL exist and correctly copy all nested fields including `Spec.TargetPort` slice\n139: \n140: #### Scenario: DeepCopyInto for AgentRuntimeList\n141: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go`\n142: - **WHEN** examining generated code\n143: - **THEN** `func (in *AgentRuntimeList) DeepCopyInto(out *AgentRuntimeList)` SHALL exist and correctly copy `Items` slice\n144: \n145: #### Scenario: DeepCopyInto for AgentRuntimeSpec\n146: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go`\n147: - **WHEN** examining generated code\n148: - **THEN** `func (in *AgentRuntimeSpec) DeepCopyInto(out *AgentRuntimeSpec)` SHALL exist\n149: \n150: #### Scenario: DeepCopyInto for TargetPort\n151: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go`\n152: - **WHEN** examining generated code\n153: - **THEN** `func (in *TargetPort) DeepCopyInto(out *TargetPort)` SHALL exist\n154: \n155: #### Scenario: DeepCopyInto for AgentRuntimeStatus\n156: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go`\n157: - **WHEN** examining generated code\n158: - **THEN** `func (in *AgentRuntimeStatus) DeepCopyInto(out *AgentRuntimeStatus)` SHALL exist\n159: \n160: ---\n161: \n162: ### Requirement: CRD generation\n163: \n164: The system SHALL generate CRD YAML that matches the expected schema from `manifests/charts/base/crds/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml`.\n165: \n166: #### Scenario: CRD generation command\n167: - **GIVEN** the repository with types defined in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n168: - **WHEN** running `make gen-crd`\n169: - **THEN** the command SHALL invoke `controller-gen crd paths=./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/... output:dir=manifests/charts/base/crds`\n170: \n171: #### Scenario: Generated CRD metadata\n172: - **GIVEN** the generated `manifests/charts/base/crds/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml`\n173: - **WHEN** examining the CRD\n174: - **THEN** `metadata.name` SHALL be `agentruntimes.runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n175: - AND `spec.group` SHALL be `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n176: - AND `spec.names.kind` SHALL be `AgentRuntime`\n177: - AND `spec.names.plural` SHALL be `agentruntimes`\n178: - AND `spec.scope` SHALL be `Namespaced`\n179: \n180: #### Scenario: Generated CRD version\n181: - **GIVEN** the generated CRD\n182: - **WHEN** examining `spec.versions`\n183: - **THEN** there SHALL be exactly one version with `name: v1alpha1`, `served: true`, and `storage: true`\n184: \n185: #### Scenario: Generated CRD spec schema\n186: - **GIVEN** the generated CRD\n187: - **WHEN** examining `spec.versions[0].schema.openAPIV3Schema.properties.spec`\n188: - **THEN** the `required` array SHALL include `maxSessionDuration`, `sessionTimeout`, `targetPort`, and `podTemplate`\n189: - AND `properties.maxSessionDuration.default` SHALL be `\"8h\"`\n190: - AND `properties.sessionTimeout.default` SHALL be `\"15m\"`\n191: \n192: #### Scenario: Generated CRD status subresource\n193: - **GIVEN** the generated CRD\n194: - **WHEN** examining `spec.versions[0]`\n195: - **THEN** `subresources.status` SHALL be present\n196: \n197: ---\n198: \n199: ### Requirement: Client-go code generation compatibility\n200: \n201: The system SHALL define types compatible with `k8s.io/code-generator` for generating typed clients, informers, and listers.\n202: \n203: #### Scenario: Group version registration for client-gen\n204: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go`\n205: - **WHEN** reading the file\n206: - **THEN** `SchemeBuilder` SHALL be defined using `NewSchemeBuilder` and `AddToScheme` SHALL be exposed as `localSchemeBuilder.AddToScheme(scheme)`\n207: \n208: #### Scenario: Types implement runtime.Object\n209: - **GIVEN** the `AgentRuntime` and `AgentRuntimeList` types\n210: - **WHEN** the DeepCopy methods are generated\n211: - **THEN** both types SHALL implement `runtime.Object` interface via `DeepCopyObject()` method\n212: \n213: #### Scenario: Client generation command\n214: - **GIVEN** types in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n215: - **WHEN** running `make gen-client`\n216: - **THEN** `hack/update-codegen.sh` SHALL be invoked, which runs `k8s.io/code-generator` v0.34.1 with:\n217:   - `--with-watch` flag\n218:   - `--output-dir client-go`\n219:   - `--output-pkg github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go`\n220:   - Input API at `runtime/v1alpha1`\n221: \n222: #### Scenario: Generated typed client exists\n223: - **GIVEN** client-go code generation completed\n224: - **WHEN** examining `client-go/clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go`\n225: - **THEN** `AgentRuntimeInterface` SHALL define methods: `Create`, `Update`, `UpdateStatus`, `Delete`, `DeleteCollection`, `Get`, `List`, `Watch`, `Patch`\n226: \n227: #### Scenario: Generated informer exists\n228: - **GIVEN** client-go code generation completed\n229: - **WHEN** examining `client-go/informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go`\n230: - **THEN** `AgentRuntimeInformer` interface SHALL define `Informer() cache.SharedIndexInformer` and `Lister() runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeLister`\n231: \n232: #### Scenario: Generated lister exists\n233: - **GIVEN** client-go code generation completed\n234: - **WHEN** examining `client-go/listers/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go`\n235: - **THEN** `AgentRuntimeLister` interface SHALL define `List(selector labels.Selector)` and `AgentRuntimes(namespace string)` methods\n\n(End of file - total 235 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Delta Spec: AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime Type Definition\n\n**Module:** `pkg/apis`  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** S\n\n---\n\n## GIVEN/WHEN/THEN Scenarios\n\n### Requirement: Package structure and registration\n\nThe system SHALL define the `AgentRuntime` and `AgentRuntimeList` types in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` with proper package structure, scheme registration, and CRD markers for controller-gen.\n\n#### Scenario: Package structure exists\n- **GIVEN** the repository root at `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube`\n- **WHEN** examining `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n- **THEN** the directory SHALL contain:\n  - `doc.go` with `+k8s:deepcopy-gen=package` marker\n  - `register.go` with `SchemeGroupVersion` set to `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/deployment/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775847426927,"end":1775847426942}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775847426947,"sessionID":"ses_2873fd99bffeD3IZMIHmfvsaUp","part":{"id":"prt_d78c14b15001bBQuqljadDR6O0","messageID":"msg_d78c12c17001JBR4q7SEYMXhbg","sessionID":"ses_2873fd99bffeD3IZMIHmfvsaUp","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-ac54000e290f4ebcaf1f82b12b6504ff","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-007: K8s Reconciler 控制器\n2: \n3: ## 概述\n4: \n5: | 属性 | 值 |\n6: |------|-----|\n7: | AR | AR-007 |\n8: | Module | pkg/workloadmanager |\n9: | Language | Go |\n10: | Size | L |\n11: \n12: ---\n13: \n14: ## 1. Purpose (目的)\n15: \n16: 实现一个 Kubernetes Reconciler 控制器，用于管理 `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1` API 组下的自定义资源：\n17: \n18: - **AgentRuntime**: 管理 Agent 运行时实例的生命周期\n19: - **CodeInterpreter**: 管理代码解释器实例的生命周期\n20: \n21: 控制器将：\n22: 1. 监听 CRD 资源的创建、更新、删除事件\n23: 2. 根据 CR spec 协调实际状态向期望状态收敛\n24: 3. 管理底层 Pod、Service、ConfigMap 等工作负载资源\n25: 4. 更新 CR status 以反映当前状态\n26: \n27: ---\n28: \n29: ## 2. Scope (范围)\n30: \n31: ### 2.1 In Scope\n32: \n33: 1. **Controller 框架搭建**\n34:    - 使用 `controller-runtime` 框架 (sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime)\n35:    - 集成 client-go 生成的客户端代码\n36:    - 实现 Reconcile 循环\n37: \n38: 2. **AgentRuntime 控制器**\n39:    - 监听 AgentRuntime CR 的变更\n40:    - 创建/更新/删除关联的 Kubernetes 资源 (Pod, Service, ConfigMap, Secret)\n41:    - 状态同步：Phase, Conditions, PodStatus, Endpoint 等\n42:    - 支持多副本部署策略\n43: \n44: 3. **CodeInterpreter 控制器**\n45:    - 监听 CodeInterpreter CR 的变更\n46:    - 管理解释器容器的生命周期\n47:    - 状态同步：Phase, Conditions, ResourceUsage 等\n48: \n49: 4. **通用功能**\n50:    - Event 记录 (Normal/Warning)\n51:    - Finalizer 处理 (资源清理)\n52:    - OwnerReference 设置 (级联删除)\n53:    - 领导选举 (Leader Election) 支持多实例部署\n54: \n55: ### 2.2 Out of Scope\n56: \n57: - Webhook (Validating/Mutating) - 由独立 AR 处理\n58: - CRD 定义本身 - 假设已存在\n59: - 具体业务逻辑 (Agent 执行、解释器逻辑) - 由其他模块处理\n60: - 监控指标暴露 - 由独立 AR 处理\n61: \n62: ---\n63: \n64: ## 3. Impact Analysis (影响分析)\n65: \n66: ### 3.1 新增文件\n67: \n68: ```\n69: pkg/workloadmanager/\n70: ├── controller.go              # 控制器入口，注册 Manager\n71: ├── agentruntime_controller.go # AgentRuntime Reconciler 实现\n72: ├── codeinterpreter_controller.go # CodeInterpreter Reconciler 实现\n73: ├── reconciler.go              # 通用 Reconciler 辅助函数\n74: ├── status.go                  # 状态更新辅助函数\n75: ├── resource_builder.go        # Kubernetes 资源构建器\n76: ├── predicates.go              # Event 过滤谓词\n77: └── suite_test.go              # 控制器集成测试\n78: ```\n79: \n80: ### 3.2 依赖关系\n81: \n82: ```\n83: pkg/workloadmanager\n84:     ├── github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go (已生成)\n85:     ├── sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime (需引入)\n86:     ├── k8s.io/api\n87:     ├── k8s.io/apimachinery\n88:     └── k8s.io/client-go\n89: ```\n90: \n91: ### 3.3 与现有模块交互\n92: \n93: | 模块 | 交互方式 |\n94: |------|----------|\n95: | pkg/apis/runtime | 读取 CR 类型定义 |\n96: | client-go | 使用生成的 Clientset、Informer、Lister |\n97: | cmd/manager | 作为控制器入口点启动 |\n98: \n99: ### 3.4 风险与缓解\n100: \n101: | 风险 | 影响 | 缓解措施 |\n102: |------|------|----------|\n103: | 控制器重启导致短暂不可用 | Medium | 使用 Leader Election 确保单实例 |\n104: | CRD 版本兼容性 | Low | 使用 apiVersion 检查 + conversion webhook |\n105: | 大规模资源性能问题 | Medium | 使用 Informer 缓存 + WorkQueue 限流 |\n106: \n107: ---\n108: \n109: ## 4. Alternatives Considered (备选方案)\n110: \n111: ### 4.1 方案 A: controller-runtime (推荐)\n112: \n113: **实现方式**: 使用 sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime 框架\n114: \n115: **优点**:\n116: - Kubernetes 官方推荐方案\n117: - 内置 Informer、WorkQueue、Leader Election\n118: - 与 kubebuilder 生态兼容\n119: - 社区活跃，文档完善\n120: - 原生支持 webhook\n121: \n122: **缺点**:\n123: - 框架较重，学习曲线稍陡\n124: - 调试复杂度高\n125: \n126: ### 4.2 方案 B: client-go 原生实现\n127: \n128: **实现方式**: 使用 client-go 的 Informer + WorkQueue 手写控制器\n129: \n130: **优点**:\n131: - 完全控制实现细节\n132: - 无额外依赖\n133: - 更轻量\n134: \n135: **缺点**:\n136: - 需要手写大量样板代码\n137: - 需要自己实现 Leader Election\n138: - 维护成本高\n139: - 与社区最佳实践脱节\n140: \n141: ### 4.3 方案 C: KUDO\n142: \n143: **实现方式**: 使用 KUDO (Kubernetes Universal Declarative Operator)\n144: \n145: **优点**:\n146: - 声明式操作定义\n147: - 内置状态机\n148: \n149: **缺点**:\n150: - 项目已停止维护\n151: - 学习成本高\n152: - 不适合简单控制器\n153: \n154: ### 4.4 方案选择\n155: \n156: **选择方案 A (controller-runtime)**\n157: \n158: 理由:\n159: 1. 官方推荐，社区支持好\n160: 2. 与现有 client-go 生成的代码无缝集成\n161: 3. 为后续 webhook、monitor 集成铺路\n162: 4. 降低维护成本\n163: \n164: ---\n165: \n166: ## 5. 设计要点\n167: \n168: ### 5.1 Reconcile 循环伪代码\n169: \n170: ```go\n171: func (r *AgentRuntimeReconciler) Reconcile(ctx context.Context, req ctrl.Request) (ctrl.Result, error) {\n172:     // 1. 获取 CR\n173:     ar := &runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime{}\n174:     if err := r.Client.Get(ctx, req.NamespacedName, ar); err != nil {\n175:         return ctrl.Result{}, client.IgnoreNotFound(err)\n176:     }\n177: \n178:     // 2. 检查 DeletionTimestamp (Finalizer 处理)\n179:     if !ar.DeletionTimestamp.IsZero() {\n180:         return r.handleDeletion(ctx, ar)\n181:     }\n182: \n183:     // 3. 确保 Finalizer 存在\n184:     if err := r.ensureFinalizer(ctx, ar); err != nil {\n185:         return ctrl.Result{}, err\n186:     }\n187: \n188:     // 4. 同步期望状态\n189:     result, err := r.sync(ctx, ar)\n190:     if err != nil {\n191:         return ctrl.Result{}, err\n192:     }\n193: \n194:     // 5. 更新 Status\n195:     if err := r.updateStatus(ctx, ar); err != nil {\n196:         return ctrl.Result{}, err\n197:     }\n198: \n199:     return result, nil\n200: }\n201: ```\n202: \n203: ### 5.2 状态机\n204: \n205: ```\n206: ┌─────────┐    Create    ┌─────────┐\n207: │  None   │ ──────────> │ Pending │\n208: └─────────┘             └────┬────┘\n209:                              │\n210:                         PodCreated\n211:                              │\n212:                              v\n213:                        ┌─────────┐\n214:                        │ Running │\n215:                        └────┬────┘\n216:                             │\n217:                     Failed/Succeeded\n218:                             │\n219:                             v\n220:                       ┌──────────┐\n221:                       │ Terminated│\n222:                       └──────────┘\n223: ```\n224: \n225: ---\n226: \n227: ## 6. 实施计划\n228: \n229: | 阶段 | 内容 | 预估工时 |\n230: |------|------|----------|\n231: | P1 | 搭建 controller-runtime 框架 | 2d |\n232: | P2 | 实现 AgentRuntime 控制器 | 3d |\n233: | P3 | 实现 CodeInterpreter 控制器 | 2d |\n234: | P4 | 单元测试 + 集成测试 | 2d |\n235: | P5 | Leader Election + 监控 | 1d |\n236: \n237: **总计**: ~10 人天\n238: \n239: ---\n240: \n241: ## 7. 参考文档\n242: \n243: - controller-runtime: https://pkg.go.dev/sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime\n244: - client-go 生成的代码: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/client-go/`\n245: - Kubebuilder Book: https://book.kubebuilder.io/\n\n(End of file - total 245 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-007: K8s Reconciler 控制器\n\n## 概述\n\n| 属性 | 值 |\n|------|-----|\n| AR | AR-007 |\n| Module | pkg/workloadmanager |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | L |\n\n---\n\n## 1. Purpose (目的)\n\n实现一个 Kubernetes Reconciler 控制器，用于管理 `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1` API 组下的自定义资源：\n\n- **AgentRuntime**: 管理 Agent 运行时实例的生命周期\n- **CodeInterpreter**: 管理代码解释器实例的生命周期\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775847426931,"end":1775847426944}}}}
